{"tid":2496489,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"NASA機智號無人機火星升空三米首飛","createTime":"2021-04-20T00:47:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-20T01:04:45.000Z","uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b773efb84baac0b878a63481fe60480a3c5e73b","tid":2496489,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T00:47:28.000Z","msg":"火星無人直升機「機智號」（Ingenuity）在本港時間昨日下午3時半，實現人造飛行器首次在另一個星球飛行的壯舉，美國太空總署（NASA）形容今次試飛，堪比117年前萊特兄弟在北卡羅來納州創下人類第一次駕駛飛機翱翔天際，具有劃時代意義。<br />\n....<br />\n今次試飛成功後，NASA計劃未來一個月內，安排「機智號」進行最多五次的飛行任務，難度、高度、航程會逐次遞增。目前，人類探索其他星體的表面，主要依靠無人四驅車，但「機智號」將會帶來革命性的變化，讓NASA可以用航拍方式，接近過去四驅車難以到達的地形進行勘察。<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210420/KUFGL6JSDVGEXOWG76CFHZ3F7Q/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210420%2FKUFGL6JSDVGEXOWG76CFHZ3F7Q%2F&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuLyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=994a0f4c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20210420%2FKUFGL6JSDVGEXOWG76CFHZ3F7Q%2F&h=780aa176\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20210420/KUFGL6JSDVGEXOWG76CFHZ3F7Q/</a>"},{"pid":"411d5d3e85154ffd2a95d204547ae26d86415c8b","tid":2496489,"uid":132859,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T00:47:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/physicsJ/status/1384103506638868482?s=19\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FphysicsJ%2Fstatus%2F1384103506638868482%3Fs%3D19&d=gloDjMIS9Xq41mamnCswuLyOm5tzSGwlZJ%2FCF8Wpw90%3D&h=bf6612da\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FphysicsJ%2Fstatus%2F1384103506638868482%3Fs%3D19&h=ca2d4001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/physicsJ/status/1384103506638868482?s=19</a>"},{"pid":"8a8057a44e2a1844134acdfa471f5c32209b70dc","tid":2496489,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-20T01:04:45.000Z","msg":"點解